<div class="project-item">
    <h3>{{#if displayDelete}}Delete{{else}}Leave{{/if}} Project</h3>
    <div>
        {{#if private}}

        <p>This is your default project which cannot be deleted.</p>

        {{else}}
            {{#if isAdmin}}
            <p>Once the project is deleted, all stacks will be<br/>removed and all apps will be forgotten (Resources will be left as they are).</p>
            <p>You can export stacks to JSON before deleting the project.</p>
            <button class="btn btn-red icon-delete" id="delete-project">Delete Project</button>
            {{/if}}
            {{#if isMember}}
            <p>By leaving this project, you wonâ€™t have access to project assets any more.</p>
            <button class="btn btn-red icon-delete" id="leave-project">Leave Project</button>
            {{/if}}
        {{/if}}
    </div>

</div>

<!--{{confirmToDelete}}-->
<p>This action CANNOT be reverted.<br/>Type the project name below to confirm deleting the project.</p>
<input type="text" class="input" id="confirm-project-name"/>

<!--{{confirmToLeave}}-->
<p>This action CANNOT be reverted.<br/>Are you sure you want to leave this project?</p>

<!--{{loading}}-->
<div class="loading-spinner"></div>


